<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bʿd ạlrḥlẗ wạlmsẖwạr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bʿd ạlrḥlẗ wạlmsẖwạr hạtbqy̱ ạlfrḥẗ hnạk fy ạldạr
 yswʿ yjlsnạ kmạn ykẖdmnạ wyhnynạ mʿ ạlạ̉brạr
 ạlqrạr- wjwạyz mʿhạ mkạfật hạnạkẖdhạ hnạk fy ạlsmwạt
 lmạ ynạdynạ bạ̉smạynạ ʿlynạ ywzʿ ạ̉ḥly̱ hbạt
 2- dh lkl tạjr bnjạḥ bạlwznẗ yḥqq ạ̉rbạḥ
 dh bạ̹klylh rạḥ ythny̱ whnạk tktr lyh ạlạ̉frạḥ
 3- wạlly hạyrbḥ ạ̉jrh tẖmyn qd ạlwznẗ hạyạkẖd ạ̹tnyn
 wạ̉ḥly̱ wạ̉ḥly̱ yswʿ hạyqwl lh nʿm nʿm yạ ʿbd ạ̉myn</lyrics>
<hymn_number>3428</hymn_number>
</song>